Dance the Night Away at  BARunch
Friday August 29th
Sunday may 8th
Every Friday
Experience the magic of dancing every  Friday night! Mixing 80's freestyle.  Let loose and dance the night away until 11 PM. Indulge in delicious food served from 7 to 9:30 PM, and enjoy refreshing drinks available from 7 PM to 11 PM. Don't miss out on a fantastic night of rhythm, fun, and great company!
07:00 PM - 11:00 PM
Fancy Flamingo Wine Glass Paint Party
Thursday September 11th
Sunday may 8th
Come join us for another fun paint and sip.  We will be painting a Fancy Flamingo on a wine glass. All supplies are included food and drinks will be served. This event sells out quick so don’’t delay get your tickets today.  Tickets can only be purchased through the link below or in person. See everyone there
